"Relative" means any of the following who are related to an individual by blood, marriage, or adoption:
A spouse;
A child;
A sibling;
A parent;
A grandparent;
A grandchild;
A stepparent;
A stepchild;
A stepsibling;
An aunt; or
An uncle.

"Trust account" means an account that is:
Established in a financial institution that is federally insured;
Separate from the debt management services provider's operating account;
Designated as a "trust account" or by another appropriate designation indicating that the funds in the account are not the funds of the licensee or its officers, employees, or agents;
Unavailable to creditors of the debt management services provider; and
Used to hold funds paid by consumers to a debt management services provider for disbursement to creditors of the consumers.
